        <updated>2021-04-07T14:05:22.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- more -->
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617807575329.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<!-- more -->
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617804341566.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<!-- more -->
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617804353641.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<!-- more -->
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">对</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">比</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">图</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">对比图
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">对</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">比</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">图</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<hr>
<p><strong>前期的准备：</strong><br>
● 一张黑色卡纸 一台相机 <s>就够了</s><br>
● 尽量避免阳光强烈的天气</p>
<p><strong>拍摄思路：</strong><br>
阴天的午后，以黑色为底色的花朵细节图，保持画面的干净与简洁</p>
<p><strong>拍摄器材：</strong><br>
索尼a6300 / 30 1.4</p>
<p><strong>后期：</strong><br>
<img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617862734777.jpg" width="50%"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">以</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">这</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">张</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">图</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">片</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">为</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">调</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">色</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">案</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">例</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">以这张图片为调色案例
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">以</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">这</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">张</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">图</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">片</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">为</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">调</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">色</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">案</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">例</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<hr>
<p><img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617865362782.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
原图颜色发灰并且有点过曝，主要调色思路是压暗高光，提亮阴影，使图片的中的花像泛光一样<br>
● 首先导入Ps复制一层备用，进入Ps的<code>Camera Raw</code>简单的调整一下基本参数<br>
● 这里我们将<code>高光</code>多压低一些，<code>阴影</code>不要拉太高，使画面稍微暗下来<br>
● 由于我们想要的效果是纯黑背景，所以这里我们要把<code>黑色</code>拉到最低，使整个画面的背景色黑透，也方便了后续的抠图和修整<br>
● 此时我们会发现整张花的<code>对比度</code>会很高，看上去很不舒服，把<code>对比度</code>降下来</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">—————————
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617867112863.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
● 之后再把<code>自然饱和度</code>也降下去，现在整张图的感觉就来了   <s>但还没结束</s></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">—————————
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617876870076.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
● 接下来把<code>纹理</code>和<code>清晰度</code>提高，增加花的质感和锐度<br>
● 因为这张对焦有点虚，所以我把<code>去除薄雾</code>拉到了最高，大家可以根据自己的图片适当更改</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">—————————
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617877824473.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
这一步调整<code>曲线</code>，使花瓣泛有珠光的感觉<br>
● 调整<code>点曲线</code>，中间调压暗，提亮高光和白色的中间调，具体参数看一下上面的图，再根据自己的情况进行调整<br>
● 调整<code>参数曲线</code>，这个还是根据自己的图片，细微调整</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">—————————
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617880321598.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
最后就是调色了<code>[混色器]</code>，这张图我只动了红黄橙<br>
● 把<code>红色饱和度</code>拉高，压暗<code>明度</code>，红色不要过亮<br>
● 把<code>橙色</code>往<code>黄色</code>偏一点，使画面颜色不单一，压暗<code>饱和度</code>与提亮<code>明度</code>，让花看上去更通透<br>
● <code>黄色饱和度</code>降低并往<code>橙色</code>偏，这里是让花旁边的叶子不那么抢眼</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">—————————
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617882540883.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
到这里差不多就结束了<br>
根据自己的喜好调整一下<code>色相/饱和度</code></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">—————————
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>把花的枝干涂抹掉就好啦 ⇓<br>
<img src="https://qfxl2001.github.io/post-images/1617881312760.jpg" width="50%"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">—</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">—————————
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span><span class="mord" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">—</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><strong>总结：</strong><br>
● 这里的调色主旨就是提亮阴影，压暗高光，再二次提亮<br>
● 曲线调节很重要，基本上是一张图的灵魂<br>
● 后期的混色器要注意，尽量参考色卡，保持色调的统一协调或者不要出现过多的杂色使画面杂乱<br>
● 还是得跟着感觉走<br>
● 前期拍摄时可以稍微欠曝一点，后期调色时更有感觉</p>
<p>欢迎交流<a href="https://qm.qq.com/cgi-bin/qm/qr?k=lcQTux5tkPLHc7zG7Ge8ct1by_Rfp1lR&amp;noverify=0">qq联系我</a><br>
差不多就这样，拜拜</p>
<p>2021年4月8日 星期四 20:03</p>
]]></content>
